#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:21
msgid "`kv_load_failure_policy`: KV Load Failure Handling Policy"
msgstr "`kv_load_failure_policy`：KV 加载失败处理策略"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:23
msgid "`kv_load_failure_policy` is a top-level field in `kv-transfer-config`."
msgstr "`kv_load_failure_policy` 是 `kv-transfer-config` 中的顶级字段。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:25
msgid ""
"`recompute`: When KV loading fails, vLLM rolls the request back to the last "
"valid prefix and reschedules it to recompute the failed KV blocks. Hybrid "
"attention models (e.g. DeepSeekV4, Qwen 3.5) are not supported yet."
msgstr ""
"`recompute`：当 KV 加载失败时，vLLM 将请求回滚到最后一个有效前缀，并重新调度以重新计算失败的 KV 块。混合注意力模型（例如 "
"DeepSeekV4、Qwen 3.5）尚不支持。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:26
msgid ""
"`fail`: When KV loading fails, the affected request is terminated directly "
"with an error."
msgstr "`fail`：当 KV 加载失败时，受影响的请求将直接终止并返回错误。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:28
msgid ""
"The default value in vLLM is `fail`. If you want the request to fall back to"
" recomputation after a KV load failure, set it to `recompute`."
msgstr "vLLM 中的默认值为 `fail`。如果希望在 KV 加载失败后请求回退到重新计算，请将其设置为 `recompute`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:30
msgid ""
"When `MultiConnector` is used, configure `kv_load_failure_policy` on the "
"`MultiConnector` top-level `kv-transfer-config` instead of the child "
"connectors."
msgstr ""
"使用 `MultiConnector` 时，请在 `MultiConnector` 顶级 `kv-transfer-config` 上配置 "
"`kv_load_failure_policy`，而不是在子连接器上配置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:32
msgid ""
"`kv_connector_extra_config`: Additional Configurable Parameters for Pooling"
msgstr "`kv_connector_extra_config`：池化的额外可配置参数"

