#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:160
msgid ""
"`eviction_high_watermark_ratio` determines the watermark where Mooncake "
"Store will perform eviction, and `eviction_ratio` determines the portion of "
"stored objects that would be evicted. `default_kv_lease_ttl` controls the "
"default lease TTL for KV objects (milliseconds); configure it via "
"`--default_kv_lease_ttl` and keep it larger than `ASCEND_CONNECT_TIMEOUT` "
"and `ASCEND_TRANSFER_TIMEOUT`."
msgstr ""
"`eviction_high_watermark_ratio` 决定了 Mooncake Store 执行驱逐（eviction）的水位线，而 "
"`eviction_ratio` 决定了将被驱逐的已存储对象的比例。`default_kv_lease_ttl` 控制 KV 对象的默认租约 "
"TTL（毫秒）；通过 `--default_kv_lease_ttl` 配置它，并使其大于 `ASCEND_CONNECT_TIMEOUT` 和 "
"`ASCEND_TRANSFER_TIMEOUT`。"

