"master startup command. For example:"
msgstr ""
"按照[运行 Mooncake Master](#run-mooncake-master) 中的描述启动 Mooncake master。要启用 SSD "
"卸载，请在相同的 master 启动命令中添加 `--enable_offload=true`。例如："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "Field"
msgstr "字段"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`enable_offload`"
msgstr "`enable_offload`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Set to `true` to enable SSD offload in Mooncake master. Keep the master port"
" aligned with `master_server_address` in `mooncake.json`."
msgstr ""
"设置为 `true` 以在 Mooncake master 中启用 SSD 卸载。保持 master 端口与 `mooncake.json` 中的 "
"`master_server_address` 一致。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`client_ttl`"
msgstr "`client_ttl`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Seconds a client stays alive after the last Ping. CLI default is `10`; see "
"[SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND with SSD offload](#121-segment_not_found-with-ssd-"
"offload)."
msgstr ""
"客户端在最后一次 Ping 后保持存活的秒数。CLI 默认值为 `10`；请参见 [SSD 卸载时的 "
"SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND](#121-segment_not_found-with-ssd-offload)。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:450
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "配置"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:452
msgid ""
"Starting from the `mooncake.json` configured in [Run Mooncake Master](#run-"
"mooncake-master), add the following SSD offload fields:"
msgstr ""
"从[运行 Mooncake Master](#run-mooncake-master) 中配置的 `mooncake.json` 开始，添加以下 SSD"
" 卸载字段："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`enable_ssd_offload`"
msgstr "`enable_ssd_offload`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Set to `true` to enable SSD offload. Environment variables are not "
"supported."
msgstr "设置为 `true` 以启用 SSD 卸载。不支持环境变量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`ssd_offload_path`"
msgstr "`ssd_offload_path`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"**Required when `enable_ssd_offload` is `true`.** Absolute path to a local "
"directory where Mooncake stores offloaded KV data (for example, "
"`/nvme/mooncake_offload`). The directory must exist and be writable by the "
"vLLM process; create it before startup (`mkdir -p <path>`). Relative paths, "
"symbolic links, and paths containing `..` are rejected by Mooncake. Passed "
"to `MooncakeDistributedStore.setup()` as the SSD storage root (equivalent to"
" `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_FILE_STORAGE_PATH` in standalone clients). Configure this"
" field in `mooncake.json` only; environment variables are not supported."
msgstr ""
"**当 `enable_ssd_offload` 为 `true` 时必填。** Mooncake 存储卸载的 KV "
"数据的本地目录的绝对路径（例如，`/nvme/mooncake_offload`）。该目录必须存在且可由 vLLM "
"进程写入；请在启动前创建它（`mkdir -p <path>`）。Mooncake 会拒绝相对路径、符号链接以及包含 `..` 的路径。该值作为 SSD"
" 存储根目录传递给 `MooncakeDistributedStore.setup()`（相当于独立客户端中的 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_FILE_STORAGE_PATH`）。仅在 `mooncake.json` 中配置此字段；不支持环境变量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:466
msgid "Running the Embedded Real Client"
msgstr "运行嵌入式真实客户端"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:468
msgid ""
"With Mode A (Embedded Real Client), Mooncake is embedded in vLLM. When the "
"vLLM service starts, `AscendStoreConnector` / `MooncakeBackend` "
"automatically calls `MooncakeDistributedStore.setup()` using the settings in"
" `mooncake.json` (including `enable_ssd_offload` and `ssd_offload_path` when"
" SSD offload is enabled). No separate `mooncake_client` process is required."
msgstr ""
"在模式 A（嵌入式真实客户端）下，Mooncake 嵌入在 vLLM 中。当 vLLM 服务启动时，`AscendStoreConnector` / "
"`MooncakeBackend` 会使用 `mooncake.json` 中的设置（包括启用 SSD 卸载时的 "
"`enable_ssd_offload` 和 `ssd_offload_path`）自动调用 "
"`MooncakeDistributedStore.setup()`。无需单独的 `mooncake_client` 进程。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:470
msgid "SSD Disk Usage Control"
msgstr "SSD 磁盘使用控制"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:472
msgid ""
"The following environment variables control disk space usage for SSD offload"
" (bucket backend):"
msgstr "以下环境变量控制 SSD 卸载（bucket 后端）的磁盘空间使用："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "Environment Variable"
msgstr "环境变量"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "Default"
msgstr "默认值"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`"
msgstr "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`1342177280` (1280 MB)"
msgstr "`1342177280`（1280 MB）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"Per-rank SSD read/write buffer size in bytes. **Not** configurable in "
"`mooncake.json`. If you hit `BUFFER_OVERFLOW`, increase this value — see "
"[Sizing MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES](#123-sizing-"
"mooncake_offload_local_buffer_size_bytes). **On A3 with "
"`ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1`, must be aligned to 1GB and counts toward "
"per-rank fabric mem quota (see [Fabric memory size alignment](#122-fabric-"
"memory-size-alignment-a3--ascend_enable_use_fabric_mem1))**."
msgstr ""
"每个 rank 的 SSD 读/写缓冲区大小（字节）。**不可**在 `mooncake.json` 中配置。如果遇到 "
"`BUFFER_OVERFLOW`，请增大此值——请参见 [调整 MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES "
"的大小](#123-sizing-mooncake_offload_local_buffer_size_bytes)。**在启用了 "
"`ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1` 的 A3 上，必须按 1GB 对齐，并计入每个 rank 的 fabric "
"内存配额（请参见 [Fabric 内存大小对齐](#122-fabric-memory-size-alignment-a3--"
"ascend_enable_use_fabric_mem1)）**。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_MAX_TOTAL_SIZE`"
msgstr "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_MAX_TOTAL_SIZE`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`0`"
msgstr "`0`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Eviction threshold in bytes. When set to `0`, the backend uses **90% of the "
"physical disk capacity** as the quota. Set an explicit value to control disk"
" usage precisely."
msgstr "以字节为单位的驱逐阈值。当设置为 `0` 时，后端使用**物理磁盘容量的 90%** 作为配额。设置显式值以精确控制磁盘使用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_EVICTION_POLICY`"
msgstr "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_EVICTION_POLICY`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`none`"
msgstr "`none`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "Eviction policy: `none` (writes fail when full), `fifo`, or `lru`."
msgstr "驱逐策略：`none`（满时写入失败）、`fifo` 或 `lru`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_TOTAL_SIZE_LIMIT_BYTES`"
msgstr "`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_TOTAL_SIZE_LIMIT_BYTES`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid "`2199023255552` (2 TB)"
msgstr "`2199023255552`（2 TB）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md
msgid ""
"**Per-rank** maximum disk usage reported to Mooncake master. Master "
"aggregates this across clients (roughly **2 TB × rank count** in the `SSD "
"Storage` total). **Always override** to match real disk capacity — the "
"default often exceeds available space."
msgstr ""
"**每 rank** 报告给 Mooncake master 的最大磁盘使用量。Master 跨客户端聚合此值（在 `SSD Storage` "
"总计中约为 **2 TB × rank 数量**）。**始终覆盖**以匹配实际磁盘容量——默认值通常超过可用空间。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:481
msgid ""
"**`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_TOTAL_SIZE_LIMIT_BYTES` risk:** If left at the 2 TB "
"default, master shows a total SSD quota far larger than the physical disk "
"(e.g. 16 ranks → ~32 TB displayed on a 1 TB NVMe). Offload still fails when "
"the disk fills, while monitoring looks healthy. Set this to your actual per-"
"rank budget before production use."
msgstr ""
"**`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_TOTAL_SIZE_LIMIT_BYTES` 风险：**如果保持 2 TB 默认值，master 显示的总 "
"SSD 配额远大于物理磁盘（例如，16 ranks → 在 1 TB NVMe 上显示约 32 "
"TB）。磁盘填满时卸载仍会失败，而监控显示正常。在生产使用前，请将此值设置为实际的每 rank 预算。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_pool.md:483
msgid ""
"Since each TP rank uses an independent SSD subdirectory (`rank_0/`, "
"`rank_1/`, ...) under `ssd_offload_path`, all ranks share the same physical "
"disk. To prevent a single rank from consuming excessive space, set an "
"explicit per-rank quota. For example, with an 800 GB disk and 8 TP ranks:"
msgstr ""
"由于每个 TP rank 在 `ssd_offload_path` 下使用独立的 SSD 子目录（`rank_0/`、`rank_1/`、...），所有"
" rank 共享同一物理磁盘。为防止单个 rank 消耗过多空间，请设置显式的每 rank 配额。例如，对于 800 GB 磁盘和 8 个 TP "
"rank："

